trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.KeyUp"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.KeyDown"></xref> routed events, as well as related attached and Preview events.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden som håndterer den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.KeyUp"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.KeyDown"> </xref> rutet hendelser, samt relaterte knyttet og forhåndsvise hendelser.

trans-unit.source: This delegate is used with the following attached events: - <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> This delegate is also used with the following routed events on base elements.
trans-unit.target: Denne representanten brukes med følgende vedlagte hendelser:- <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>Denne representanten brukes også med følgende rutet hendelser for base elementer.</xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Input.Keyboard.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: These routed events forward the previously listed attached events to make them more accessible to the general element model in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Disse rutet hendelsene videresende er oppført ovenfor vedlagte hendelsene for å gjøre dem mer tilgjengelig for generell elementet modellen i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> The attached events and the base element routed events share their event data, and the bubbling and tunneling versions of the routed events also share event data.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName>Vedlagte hendelser og base elementet rutet-hendelser dele hendelsesdataene sine, og den Bobling og tunnelering versjoner av distribuert hendelsene også dele Hendelsesdata.</xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.PreviewKeyUp?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyDown?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.KeyUp?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This can affect the handled characteristics of the event as it travels the event route.
trans-unit.target: Dette kan påvirke håndtert egenskaper for hendelsen underveis hendelsen-ruten.
